<h3 id="search-for-pattern-in-all-packages-name-description-and-summary"><strong>S</strong><strong>earch for pattern in all packages name, description and summary</strong></h3>

<p>The search option checks the names, descriptions, summaries and listed package maintainers of all of the available packages to find those that match. For example, to search for all packages that relate to â€œzipâ€, type:</p>

<pre># <strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">yum search zip</span></strong>
